        Parameters:
        laboratoryId - A string that contains an id that identifies the Clinical Analysis Laboratory.
        address - A string that contains the full address of Clinical Analysis Laboratory.
        name - A string that contains the name of Clinical Analysis Laboratory.
        phoneNumber - A long that contains the phone number of Clinical Analysis Laboratory.
